steps.name: the user is on the Fortnums and Mason homepage
the user select the Non EU country switcher United Kingdom and € EUR
the user click on search button
the user fill the search field by Royal Blend Tea
the user hovers over the first product on the PLP
the user retrieves the name of the product
the user clicks on the Add to Bag button
the user gets the title of the product from the cart
the user adds the quantity 10 of the product from the cart
the user gets the price of a single product
the user moves the element to the wish list
